Wrote this caption while styling 11 sections, using 4 curl products, and diffusing for 30 minutes 😌

Tag someone who would relate 🥹💜

#curlfriendsofarata #sayitloudcurlyandproud #arata #straight_hair #curlyhaircare

INDIAN SUMMERS. 

I wanted to do something like this from a long time, I made a little old rustic setup using a Kantha bedsheet that my mom made that’s hanging in the bg, it gives a beautiful touch to the pictures plus some other sheets and a throw on a old terrace. 

It is a shoot for the shirts from @sethji_india with the help of @navni_trehan for taking these beautiful pictures. Let me know your thoughts on this. Thanks for watching 🫶🏼✨

Creative direction, styling and modelled by me @p.pushpendra 
Pictures by @navni_trehan
